<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 09:15:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>英伟达CEO黄像流行歌星一样在台湾掀起“Jensanity”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/like-pop-star-nvidias-ceo-huang-stirs-up-jensanity-taiwan-2024-06-05/</link><description>自英伟达首席执行官黄仁勋抵达台湾一周半以来，他的一举一动都受到密切关注。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 08:51:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/like-pop-star-nvidias-ceo-huang-stirs-up-jensanity-taiwan-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>电动汽车推动沃尔沃汽车 5 月销量增长 13%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-may-sales-rise-13-2024-06-05/</link><description>沃尔沃汽车周三表示，得益于欧洲销量增长 27% 以及全电动 EX30 的强劲表现，沃尔沃汽车 5 月份销量增至 68,034 辆，同比增长 13%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 07:17:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-may-sales-rise-13-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯在与巴勒斯坦对手法塔赫的会谈中展现了战后雄心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/hamas-signals-post-war-ambition-talks-with-palestinian-rival-fatah-2024-06-05/</link><description>与哈马斯和法塔赫这两个巴勒斯坦派系的五名消息人士的对话表明，本月巴勒斯坦派系哈马斯和法塔赫之间的深刻分歧将限制其和解谈判的进展，但会议强调，在以色列加沙战争后，伊斯兰组织可能会保留影响力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 06:06:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/hamas-signals-post-war-ambition-talks-with-palestinian-rival-fatah-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国将于2027年建立碳足迹管理体系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-establish-carbon-footprint-management-system-by-2027-2024-06-05/</link><description>周三，中国表示，计划到 2027 年初步建立碳足迹管理体系，此举将建立更全面、更统一的碳排放标准体系。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 05:46:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-establish-carbon-footprint-management-system-by-2027-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>Zara 母公司 Inditex 因春季销售回升而提振</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/zara-owner-inditex-reports-slowing-quarterly-sales-growth-2024-06-05/</link><description>Zara 母公司 Inditex 报告称，其春夏系列近期销量有所回升，周三该公司股价上涨，因为这家全球顶级时尚零售商公布的季度业绩符合预期。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 05:38:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/zara-owner-inditex-reports-slowing-quarterly-sales-growth-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>独家：电动汽车制造商蔚来汽车获得监管机构批准在中国建设第三家工厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ev-maker-nio-gets-regulatory-nod-third-factory-china-sources-say-2024-06-05/</link><description>三名知情人士表示，电动汽车制造商蔚来汽车已获得在中国建设第三家工厂的批准，这将使其批准的总产能提高到 100 万辆汽车，几乎与特斯拉庞大的上海工厂持平。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 05:28:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ev-maker-nio-gets-regulatory-nod-third-factory-china-sources-say-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>普华永道恒大的打击将在中国公司周围反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/breakingviews/pwc-evergrande-hit-will-ricochet-around-china-inc-2024-06-05/</link><description>中国对普华永道的“牙齿和荆棘”即将到来。虽然竞争对手已经从即将到来的惩罚中受益，但这样的决定将引起所有金融中介机构的注意。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 04:57:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/breakingviews/pwc-evergrande-hit-will-ricochet-around-china-inc-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>在另一位临时教练的带领下，韩国有望在 2026 年预选赛中晋级</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/with-another-interim-coach-helm-south-korea-look-advance-2026-qualifiers-2024-06-05/</link><description>尽管金道勋成为自今年年初以来第三位执掌亚洲重量级球队的教练，但韩国周四将迎战新加坡，只需一分即可确保晋级 2026 年世界杯亚洲区预选赛第三轮。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 04:13:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/with-another-interim-coach-helm-south-korea-look-advance-2026-qualifiers-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>随着欧洲央行会议临近，股市因降息押注而上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-05/</link><description>世界股市周三上涨，美元企稳，美国劳动力市场数据疲软，增强了美联储 9 月降息的预期，欧洲央行政策会议成为焦点。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 02:52:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>在银行诈骗中损失金钱的中国人抗议后被拘留数月</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-who-lost-money-bank-fraud-detained-months-after-protest-2024-06-05/</link><description>该报道基于路透社对抗议录像、此前未报道的逮捕通知和采访的回顾，审视了自 2022 年以来在中国激增的一场经济抗议活动，在此期间，数十万人在房地产泡沫破裂中失去了房屋并成为受害者到投资诈骗。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 02:04:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-who-lost-money-bank-fraud-detained-months-after-protest-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国强劲的服务业活动拉动就业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-robust-services-activity-drives-up-employment-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-06-05/</link><description>周三的一项私营部门调查显示，中国 5 月份服务业活动以 10 个月来最快速度加速，人员配备水平自 1 月份以来首次扩大，表明第二季度将持续复苏。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 01:49:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-robust-services-activity-drives-up-employment-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查：投资者考虑选举和美国潜在宽松政策，新兴货币并未获得缓解</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/no-relief-emerging-currencies-seen-investors-ponder-elections-potential-us-2024-06-05/</link><description>路透对货币分析师的调查显示，由于美联储不急于降息以及一些关键的全国大选结果，新兴市场货币今年将难以反弹。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 01:38:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/no-relief-emerging-currencies-seen-investors-ponder-elections-potential-us-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大央行政策会议关键数据公布前美元小幅上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-finds-footing-traders-turn-us-services-data-2024-06-05/</link><description>在美国重要经济数据公布和加拿大货币政策会议之前，美元周三企稳，交易员押注此次会议将引发全球一些最大经济体的降息周期。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 00:47:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-finds-footing-traders-turn-us-services-data-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>SEKO 赢得美国海关机构有条件恢复</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/seko-wins-conditional-reinstatements-us-customs-agency-2024-06-05/</link><description>私营公司SEKO Logistics表示，美国海关与边境保护局（CBP）已有条件恢复其对两个重要国际贸易项目的参与，但仍未确定导致暂停的违规行为。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 00:29:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/seko-wins-conditional-reinstatements-us-customs-agency-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国人工智能芯片公司降级设计以确保台积电生产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-ai-chip-firms-downgrading-designs-secure-tsmc-production-sources-say-2024-06-04/</link><description>四位知情人士表示，一些中国人工智能芯片公司现在正在设计功能较弱的处理器，以在面临美国制裁的情况下保留台积电的生产能力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 23:03:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-ai-chip-firms-downgrading-designs-secure-tsmc-production-sources-say-2024-06-04/</guid></item></channel></rss>